description: Findit, Inc. operates social media content management platform. It owns and operates Findit.com, an interactive search engine that allows members to submit URLs they want Findit to index in its search results, as well as Findit app. The company also offers content creation and distribution, web development, search engine optimization, social media, and social networking marketing campaigns; and news and press release distribution, Findit extension URLs, vanity URL, URL submissions into the Findit search engine, and social media promoted posts, as well as Findit Prime, a package of press release distribution. The company was formerly known as Artemis Energy Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Findit, Inc. in February 2015. Findit, Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Peachtree Corners, Georgia.
